{"tid":803314,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解老師會有暑假放","createTime":"2018-09-02T07:27:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-02T11:42:38.000Z","uid":198834,"like":5,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"e87733fe269a251faabb3c1ec23f52fcd388783b","tid":803314,"uid":198834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T07:27:10.000Z","msg":"好多行政、教學嘢可以暑假預備<br />\n開學咪唔使咁辛苦<br />\n真係唔明點解要出糧畀佢地放個幾月假<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 同樣唔明點解立法會同行政會議都有假放<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ba393360572da92410e16608d2cfd3bf8af79d4","tid":803314,"uid":8867,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T07:30:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e6cd7b172e56fdcfc3e65cbc87bf43045cba1095","tid":803314,"uid":77959,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T07:33:47.000Z","msg":"放一個月度咋喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我以前中學七月廿幾先有假放，定而家暑假提早咗"},{"pid":"496d1f8416bc1683a9a1e39f425dc8fe9e3dce3f","tid":803314,"uid":126729,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T07:37:06.000Z","msg":"80年代既老師<br />\n先會有同學生一齊放暑假，同學生一齊返學<br />\n<br />\n點解有暑假⋯⋯因爲老師無得請大假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實個所謂暑假，得二至三個星期。咪即係大假囉<br />\n<br />\n大假有得隨年資加<br />\n老師set 死架ching"},{"pid":"541908213529e103f818ef0d984f0ff06eaf0afe","tid":803314,"uid":198834,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"e6cd7b172e56fdcfc3e65cbc87bf43045cba1095","tid":803314,"uid":77959,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T07:33:47.000Z","msg":"放一個月度咋喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我以前中學七月廿幾先有假放，定而家暑假提早咗"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T07:42:16.000Z","msg":"想問有邊份工每年可以放一個月假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c59d4748f1918eacb1a2369ecd3d5906914aeaaa","tid